<h2>Option 2: Square </h2>
<h3>Summary</h3>
<p>Another option for an online payment processing software is <a href="https://squareup.com/us/en">Square</a>. Square is also a well known payment processing service that is used by many businesses. One downside to this option is that this service focuses more on a single business selling products, rather than multiple businesses selling products from one website. </p>


<h3>Pricing</h3>
<p>As for pricing, their model is more in-depth than Stripes pricing model but is the same as Stripe's pricing for the implementation that would be done on the website (2.9% + 0.30 for every payment you take using Square Online Store, eCommerce integrations, or online payment APIs)</p>


