<h3>Recommendation</h3>
<p>Of these two options, the Stripe payment service would be the recommended option to implement into the website. The extensive documentation they provide would allow for a faster implementation of a webstore to the site. The ability to set up a marketplace for business to sell their own products on is also an additional benefit to Stripe's software. And since both are priced at the same 2.9% + 0.30 for each transaction, there is no incentive as far as pricing to choose one over the other.</p>